OL,3,CUK cities where families 'losing
OL,4,Csignificant cash in the bin due to
OL,5,Cfood waste'
OL,7,FFamilies in Glasgow, Liverpool and
OL,8,FNottingham are particularly likely to
OL,9,Fbe wasting high amounts of money on
OL,10,Ffood that goes uneaten, a survey
OL,11,Findicates.
OL,13,FThe survey of more than 2,000 UK
OL,14,Fparents of children aged four to 12
OL,15,Ffound that 60% said their children
OL,16,Frefuse to eat a meal they are served
OL,17,Fat least once a week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784432922
OL,3,CUK cities where families 'losing
OL,4,Csignificant cash in the bin due to
OL,5,Cfood waste'
OL,7,FThe average amount that parents
OL,8,Festimated their family wasted annually
OL,9,Fon uneaten food was #283 ` with
OL,10,Ffamilies in Glasgow estimating they
OL,11,Fwaste #369 on average, according to
OL,12,Fthe research for Bernard Matthews.
OL,14,FLiverpool was another food waste
OL,15,Fhotspot in the survey, with an
OL,16,Festimated #316 wasted annually
OL,17,Ftypically by families, while in
OL,18,FNottingham, the average annual food
OL,19,Fwaste bill was found to be #315.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784432922
OL,3,CUK cities where families 'losing
OL,4,Csignificant cash in the bin due to
OL,5,Cfood waste'
OL,7,FIn London and Belfast, families were
OL,8,Falso found to be wasting more than
OL,9,F#300 per year on average on uneaten
OL,10,Ffood, according to the research,
OL,11,Fcarried out by Censuswide in May.
OL,13,FAt the other end of the spectrum,
OL,14,Ffamilies in Bristol estimated they
OL,15,Fwere wasting #198 per year typically.
OL,17,FHalf (50%) of parents surveyed felt
OL,18,Fthat encouraging their child to play
OL,19,Fwith food would help to reduce the
OL,20,Fpressure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
