OL,3,CUK cities where families 'losing
OL,4,Csignificant cash in the bin due to
OL,5,Cfood waste'
OL,7,FLaurence Hinton, head of marketing at
OL,8,FBernard Matthews, said: "Parents agree
OL,9,Fthat playing with your food can take
OL,10,Fsome of the pressure out of mealtimes,
OL,11,Fencouraging children to engage
OL,12,Fpositively with food and ultimately
OL,13,Fmaking family meals more enjoyable and
OL,14,Fless wasteful."
OL,16,FHere are the average amounts parents
OL,17,Festimate they waste on food annually
OL,18,Facross various UK cities, according to
OL,19,Fthe survey:
OL,21,FGlasgow, #369
